Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.41,0:00:06.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is the turbulent Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:11.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Warlords keep on fighting day and night over\NJipangu State, where Karakuri people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:16.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri martial artists were sharpening their swords, dreaming of victory and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:23.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,And now, a wild hero has arrived, seeking to be the number one Karakuri martial artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:33.18,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\an8\fs32\fade(770,0)}Karakuri Kengouden
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:33.18,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\fade(770,0)}Musashi Road
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:33.18,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\fs24\fade(770,0)}(The Story of {\i1}Karakuri{\i0} Martial Artist: Road of Musashi)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:38.02,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A man always dreams of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.77,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,in the center of the world to become
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.65,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,AH! AH! the strongest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:49.70,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Raise the sword of your heart high to the wide sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:54.33,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Raise the curtain to the road of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.92,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A skilled swordsman roams on Jipangu State
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:06.55,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His name is Musashi, a Karakuri man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:08.05,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Go! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:10.97,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,The sound of fierce duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:13.80,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,makes life dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:19.27,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Battles of yesterdays make you stronger today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:25.52,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:28.53,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:30.99,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,The sound of fierce duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.49,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,makes life dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:39.58,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Fight the utmost with the stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:45.84,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:51.09,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His eyes shined! Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,During their trip, Musashi and others reunited with Baiken once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:08.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,And Baiken offered hospitality in a superb mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:13.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,But their happiness didn't last long; they had to fight against a monster named Nue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:17.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,But thanks to the friendly aid from Baiken and cooperation from Kojirō,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:22.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,they took Nue under the control of Onihime down and saved Date family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:28.13,TitleEP,en,0,0,90,,Shuten Explodes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:46.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's going on at the Cursed Valley deep here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:25.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Gohachi and Heisuke that I thought to be lost are also there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,I must let villagers know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you sure that we aren't lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,My nose is working fine-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,You have zero scientific evidences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's not it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:09.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't fight over something that pointless! Let's just hurry up to an inn in a lively town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,We're not going to find one at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:13.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:23.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,This! My nose definitely works perfectly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Tasty-looking manjus-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:46.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,You, karakuri martial artist! Have a match with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,A match?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Forget it, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am not a kiddo! I am Santa! Face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,You coward! That's unforgivable, even for a child-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's because you touched the offering to Ksitigarbha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.78,Note,en,0,0,0,,(a major figure in Buddhism)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,W- what-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop right there, Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:07.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Santa is right! You were being greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:11.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,But Kojirō don't give me any allowances or buy me snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why did you give a surprise attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,I just tested your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:17.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Test?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:21.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see! You want to be a martial artist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will become a parent like my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Care to elaborate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:31.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,While you look like you're showing off, you seem to be pretty capable. You're hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:36.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's not for free, of course. Take my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is gold dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,-So, is it gold-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?\N-Those are large drops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Will you accept this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will take that instead-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,No way you're rescuing my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Tch, he's not cute at all-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:01.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Kojirō?\N-I can't let this pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:08.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,With that much gold, all that manjus, dangos, sweet red bean paste, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's going to get me a meal of lifetime-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:17.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me! I'm going too-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is it, Jiraiyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shuten wanted to pay for his failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:40.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Gold bars, eh... But this is not enough for redemption of failure of getting Senhime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:46.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,We know that well. Not only this, but also we wanted to offer you war funds of thousands and millions of ryos instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:56.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now that's a different story. A huge sum of war funds is required to take General Ieyasu down and become the shōgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:07:00.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yessir. I'll be back after making war funds with Shuten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:01.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait, Jiraiyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:08.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Leave the gold mountain to Shuten. You will keep an eye on Jūbee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jūbee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,That rat Jūbee...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:18.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is clear that he is protecting Senhime and others in shadow and observing us in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:24.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's why I'm ordering you, Jiraiyan, to find out Jūbee's traces and assassinate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,And when we take Senhime into our hands, we'll take the shōgunate down at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,And then, the world will fall into my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:42.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:49.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yeah. They went to hunt or pick mushrooms. 8 people from our village are missing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,And your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:56.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,In The Cursed Valley, there must be an evil creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:57.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:01.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hm? My nose is detecting something-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,That fish is dead-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's going on-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,The water must be toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,A evil creature must be taking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:19.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about evil creatures-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'll cut it with my dual blades-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,It was from the creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's the sound of the creature-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Leave it to me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:55.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Must be Senhime and Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,O- Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Secret sword! Tsubamegaeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:24.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will never forget the failure and the humiliation I received from them even if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:29.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Your eternal grave will take place in the Cursed Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,You will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,T- this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:55.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not come, Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,You cursed monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,You really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,My body is getting stiff-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Senhime, please hide somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Secret sword! Tsubamegaeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:18.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:33.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:40.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,One of Four Rulers of Iga, Shutentiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,You will face my wrath today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:47.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō and Musashi shall be cooked in due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:59.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Not only my dad but also everyone... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:06.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a terrible crisis! Wait for the stormy latter half!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:35.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will dispatch you as an offering along with these treasures. Behave until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Musashi... Kojirō...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:59.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,You bastards! Work properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do you want to end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hurry up and work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:34.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now, how should I cook them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:46.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:54.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see! Water washes mud away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:24.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Plucking your head off won't be enough for my grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will kill you with this, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,How does that feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see, I see! You're happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:45.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's almost there, Musashi! My chainsaw will tear off your body into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:56.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,It seems that it's touching your body. Time to break you into two pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,You! What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll face you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:31.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,What an impudent brat! I'll face you as you wished!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Santa, please take care of Kojirō of Osenchan-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:46.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're better than I thought, Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:58.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dual blades? How presumptuous of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Avira hum kham, Mohenjo-Daro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.21,Note,en,0,0,0,,(lit. Mound of the Dead; an archaeological city in Indus Valley Civilization)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're here again-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! That monster before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:14.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not gonna work anymore-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:25.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's cheating-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,I look miserable again-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,My eyes are spinning-{\i1}dasu{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,Cut it off-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! That clay warrior is made out of mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Use water to wash off mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,I got it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:01.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Chase me if you can, you pile of mud-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! How's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:38.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,I did it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shuten! Take my Tsubamegaeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:55.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Secret sword or not, that Tsubamegaeshi won't work twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Avira hum kham, rock smasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,You really did it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:23.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Using sorcery like that is cowardly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Face me with your sword like a real man-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:28.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh! Victory is what matters. Just win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,W- who was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,That brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:47.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:49.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,I can't take my sword back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Niten'ichiryū! Kanibasami no Tachi-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.93,Note,en,0,0,0,,(lit. Sword of Crab Scissors)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Showing off again? I could have dodged that myself-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,I gotta show off for at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:27.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,You bastard! Avira hum kham, hurricane form!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:38.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Go! We're rescuing Kojirō and Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,-The tornado\N-has stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Secret sword! Tsubamegaeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, Shuten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:03.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Niten'ichiryū! Jūmonjigiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:03.28,Note,en,0,0,0,,(lit. cross cut. Jū means the number ten({\fsMeiryo UI}十{\r}))
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wow, it's pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:31.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ack, it's gold-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, it's gold-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! That's such a waste-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:39.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Curse those rats... Musashi's group again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:45.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unforgivable! I will take their lives away, whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,We are sincerely grateful for all your work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kojirō and Osenchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:02.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Your father surely understands what you have felt by now, Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:05.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Hey, where's Musashi?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,All that gold we could have gotten-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:14.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm going to recover my investment by stuffing rice-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, Musashi! Stop being so gluttonous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,One more bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a gourmand he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:36.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're right. He should be practicing self-discipline, and moreover, this is a trip with an important objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm hungry... Dango... Manju...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Musashi!\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is anything wrong-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here! Your lunch box.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:51.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes! Santa's parents are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:56.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,You can't train when you're hungry. Give it your best, Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it! I'll do my best-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:04.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, are you being cocky to me, the number one of Jipangu-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:06.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:13.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thinking to help and yet ending up being helped, for the love no matter the humiliation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:17.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,a man must have a way of life of breaking through the violent wind of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:24.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wild flowers are smiling. Go, go, Musashi! Hit hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:43.93,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes the moon jumps over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:47.18,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,the pocket of empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:49.56,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Laugh loudly and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:52.18,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,morning will come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:57.52,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about losing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:01.11,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Keep going! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:03.53,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,A bare hand is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:13.62,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:21.67,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how life is! Look, a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:26.39,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,follows us wagging its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:37.31,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:45.78,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how the future is, too! Look, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:51.62,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,is opening its hands and smiling at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:08.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hot springs are the best, as we're tired from all that journey! That's why we stopped by at an inn with a hot spring-{\i1}dasu{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:11.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,but what?! There's a mountain around here where dead people's spirits gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:18.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,I met again with my beloved Ishimatsu there-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I wish him to go to heaven without getting lost-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.23,0:24:22.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next story! Woah! It's Ishimatsu's Ghost-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:26.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's a stormy great spiritual realm-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
