Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:31.08,TitleEP,en,0,0,240,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:31.08,TitleEP,en,0,0,90,,It's Ishimatsu's Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:31.08,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}Look forwards for it!